From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Quill <quill@example.com>
Date: Sat, 27 Jun 2026 18:53:01 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 19/19] fix: speed up interactive CLI startup

Keep omitted --compact as None so HermesCLI can honor display.compact. Add display.startup_banner and display.startup_status toggles for users who want the fastest path to the prompt.

For bare interactive chat, defer plugin discovery, shell-hook registration, and default platform toolset resolution until the first real agent turn. One-shot/query modes still prepare synchronously so plugin toolsets and hooks are ready before execution.

Co-authored-by: Nako <280596805+nakoagent@users.noreply.github.com>

